text: Filippo Moyersoen (born 30 August 1954) is an Italian equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Italy Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Milan
